Sara Martin, 37, from Lititz, Pennsylvania, was diagnosed with terminal brain cancer in 2010 .
She has not spoken for weeks and is being driven to Sarasota, Florida, today .
Her family is taking her there for what will likely be her final holiday .
The mother-of-three has three children - Carlie, 12, Gretchen, 11, and Carlie - with her husband Dean .
Mrs Martin, who also has a nine-year-old son, said: 'If you say 'Florida' I'll get dad to take us'